node.text:
A day outside Cotonou. 
Small summary of this beautiful day: sun, good musical atmosphere, laughter like never before. 
We arrived in Ouidah quite quickly and even if we didn't see the interior of the temple of the pythons, we went to go to Alozo Terasse where we also had a good time. 
Impeccable service with a very good welcome. What a beautiful place! Then last stop? The Zinsou Foundation with a very good decor. We'll do it soon, won't we @coraldoadj @iam_yissegnon ?
—
—
📸 @gifty_gloriane 
—
—
#vlog #bestmoments #bestdestinations #ouidah #ouidahplage #beningoodvibes #destinationvlog #melaninpoppin #brownskingirl #videooffriday #mood #alozoterrasse #likeforlikes #followforfollowback #beautifulday #beautifulplace #goodtimes #goodfriends #goodtimes

Wishes to be there forever… ❤️

This year was rich in emotions and pushed me to learn a lot of lessons. I went through all the emotions but I thank the Lord for being alive until now. I wish you a very happy holiday season, especially to enjoy your loved ones as much as you can. We see each other in 2022 with very good vibes and hoping that the new year will be filled with positivities. Happy new year guys ✨
__
__
📸 @gloria__ndanga ❤️
